body:
Clintasha Headcannon

Every now and again Clint will casually propose to Natasha. Never expecting a yes but always hoping for one he’ll say “Marry me” and Natasha will always blush but change the topic. But every now and again, while Clint is asleep or when he takes out his hearing aid Natasha will whisper “ya delayu”. Meaning “I do” in Russian.

title: Venom (2018) - Review
body:
Venom (2018) – Review

“Eyes. Lungs. Pancreas. So many snacks, so little time.”

In 2018, there was a film in which a down-on-his-luck loser was imbued with some pretty awesome powers. All of a sudden he could do some amazing things, but he had a powerful entity in his head which he constantly had to talk to and argue with. The film toed the line between action, comedy, and body horror. That film is Leigh Whannell’s…
